-
-### Pipeline Stages
-
-```
-PR opened:
-  lint → typecheck → unit tests → integration tests → preview deploy
-
-Merged to main:
-  lint → typecheck → unit tests → integration tests → build image → deploy staging → smoke tests → deploy production
-```
