-## Parametrization
-
-### Basic Parametrization
-
-```python
-@pytest.mark.parametrize("input,expected", [
-    ("hello", "HELLO"),
-    ("world", "WORLD"),
-    ("PyThOn", "PYTHON"),
-])
-def test_uppercase(input, expected):
-    """Test runs 3 times with different inputs."""
-    assert input.upper() == expected
