-
-### Multiple Parameters
-
-```python
-@pytest.mark.parametrize("a,b,expected", [
-    (2, 3, 5),
-    (0, 0, 0),
-    (-1, 1, 0),
-    (100, 200, 300),
-])
-def test_add(a, b, expected):
-    """Test addition with multiple inputs."""
-    assert add(a, b) == expected
-```
