-### Parametrize with IDs
-
-```python
-@pytest.mark.parametrize("input,expected", [
-    ("valid@email.com", True),
-    ("invalid", False),
-    ("@no-domain.com", False),
-], ids=["valid-email", "missing-at", "missing-domain"])
