-### 7. Backup & Disaster Recovery
-
-#### Automated Backups
-
-```terraform
-# PASS: CORRECT: Automated RDS backups
-resource "aws_db_instance" "main" {
-  allocated_storage     = 20
-  engine               = "postgres"
-
-  backup_retention_period = 30  # 30 days retention
-  backup_window          = "03:00-04:00"
