+**修复方案**（`src/agents/main_agent.py`）：
+
+```python
+def _trim_history(self) -> None:
+    if len(self._history) > _HISTORY_LIMIT:
+        self._history = self._history[-_HISTORY_LIMIT:]
+    while self._history and self._history[0].role == "tool":
+        self._history.pop(0)
+```
